NK016(ma)011:0: na rag dong sprugs phyag rgya gcig pa'i rgyun khyer yang zab snying po zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK016(ma)011:2: na rag dong sprugs phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor
NK016(ma)011:3: shin tu bsdus pa'i tshul gyi nyams su len pa
NK016(ma)011:7: dang po la'ang skyabs sems gnyis las /
NK016(ma)011:9: mdun gyi nam mkhar bla ma rdo rje sems dpa'
NK016(ma)011:10: skyabs gnas kun 'dus kyi ngo bor bzhugs par bsam
NK016(ma)011:12: bla ma bde gshegs 'dus pa'i sku //
NK016(ma)011:13: dkon mchog gsum gyi rang bzhin la //
NK016(ma)011:14: bdag dang 'gro drug sems can rnams //
NK016(ma)011:15: byang chub bar du skyabs su mchi //
NK016(ma)011:16: zhes skyabs su 'gro ba kun rdzob dang /
NK016(ma)011:17: mthar bla ma rang la bsdus te 'khor gsum mi
NK016(ma)011:18: dmigs pa'i ngang du mnyam par 'jog pa don dam
NK016(ma)011:19: mo // gnyis pa sems bskyed ni /
NK016(ma)011:20: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK016(ma)011:21: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK016(ma)011:22: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK016(ma)011:23: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK016(ma)011:24: zhes gzhan don du sems bskyed pa kun rdzob dang /
NK016(ma)011:25: sems bskyed pa'i sems de skye 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro
NK016(ma)011:26: 'ong dang bral ba'i ngang la sems rtse gcig tu
NK016(ma)011:27: mnyam par 'jog pa don dam mo //
NK016(ma)011:28: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gnyis /
NK016(ma)011:31: dang po lha sgom pa ni /
NK016(ma)011:32: ma h+aa shu nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)011:33: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad mi dmigs shing spros pa dang bral ba'o //
NK016(ma)011:34: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can rnams la 'dzin
NK016(ma)011:35: med sgyu ma lta bu'i snying rje mkha' khyab tu
NK016(ma)011:36: spros / stong nyid snying rje zung du 'jug pa'i
NK016(ma)011:37: rang rig a yig dkar po bde gsal stong pa
NK016(ma)011:38: nyid kyi rang bzhin du gsal ba las /
NK016(ma)011:39: h'u gi sgra gdangs nam mkha' gang bar spros pa
NK016(ma)011:40: las rdo rje'i sa gzhir gur ye shes kyi me
NK016(ma)011:41: dpung mtha' med du 'phro bas phyogs kun gtams te
NK016(ma)011:42: cis kyang mi shigs pa'i srung pa'i 'khor lor gyur
NK016(ma)011:43: pa'i nang du ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i
NK016(ma)011:44: gzhal yas khang mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs
NK016(ma)011:45: pa'i dbus su / seng ge brgyad kyis btegs pa'i
NK016(ma)011:46: rin po che'i khri pad nyi zla ba'i gdan la
NK016(ma)011:47: rang gi sems nyid a dkar po gsal ba babs
NK016(ma)011:48: pa'i dbus su / / de yongs su gyur pa las h+au yig sngon po gsal zhing 'bar ba /
NK016(ma)011:50: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs /
NK016(ma)011:51: slar 'dus yongs su gyur pa las rdo rje sngon po rtse lnga pa /
NK016(ma)011:52: de las 'od zer 'phros pas 'jig rten khams kyi
NK016(ma)011:53: thabs kyi cha thams cad bsdus te thim pa yongs
NK016(ma)011:55: rang nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog mthing ga zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK016(ma)011:56: zhi zhing rab tu 'dzum pa'i mdangs gsal ba'i zhal
NK016(ma)011:57: gyi 'gyur ba ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam par rol
NK016(ma)011:58: pa'i nyams can / mtshan dang dpe byad kyis 'bar ba /
NK016(ma)011:59: phyag g.yas rdo rjee thugs kar 'dzin cing /
NK016(ma)011:60: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK016(ma)011:61: dbu skra ral pa'i thor tshugs can /
NK016(ma)011:62: zhabs gnyis rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung gis brtan par bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)011:63: yab kyi thugs ka nas m+au chad /
NK016(ma)011:64: 'od zer 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las dril bu /
NK016(ma)011:65: de las 'od zer 'phros pas 'jig rten khams kyi
NK016(ma)011:66: shes rab kyi cha thams cad bsdus te thim pa
NK016(ma)011:68: yab kyi g.yon phyogs nye ba'i pang du yum rdo
NK016(ma)011:69: rje dbyings phyugs ma sngon mo g.yas dril bu 'dzin
NK016(ma)011:71: g.yon rdo rje rang gi thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)011:72: brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung gis 'khril ba /
NK016(ma)011:73: gnyis ka 'ang zhi ba'i rgyan chas bcu gsum gyi spras shing /
NK016(ma)011:74: zhi ba'i nyams dgu rgyas pa /
NK016(ma)011:75: 'od zer kha dog drug gi snang ba re re'ang
NK016(ma)011:76: bye ba phrag drug drug tu 'phro ba'i klong na
NK016(ma)011:77: bzhugs pa / yab yum gnyis kyi thugs kar rang
NK016(ma)011:78: 'dra'i ye shes sems dpa' rgyan dang phyag mtshan spangs
NK016(ma)011:79: pa re re'i thugs kar zla ba la h'u dang
NK016(ma)011:80: m+au yig sngon po rtag tu 'char bzhin pa /
NK016(ma)011:81: de las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis phyogs bcu dus
NK016(ma)011:82: bzhi'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa thams cad rdo
NK016(ma)011:83: rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi rnam par spyan drangs
NK016(ma)011:84: / chu la chu bzhag pa ltar rang lus la dbyer med du 'dres /
NK016(ma)011:85: slar yang thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas
NK016(ma)011:86: dbang gi lha mi bskyod pa gtso bor gyur pa'i
NK016(ma)011:87: rigs lnga yab yum gyi rnam par spyan drangs /
NK016(ma)011:88: rigs lnga yab yum gnyis su med par sbyor ba mdzad /
NK016(ma)011:89: rjes chags kyi mes zhu ba'i ye shes lnga'i chu
NK016(ma)011:90: rgyun mgo bo'i gnas lngar babs te dbang bskur bas
NK016(ma)011:92: nyon mongs pa lnga sbyangs phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su gnas gyur /
NK016(ma)011:93: chu'i lhag ma spyi bor brtan pa las mi bskyod
NK016(ma)011:94: pa bdag por gyur pa'i rigs lnga sprul sku'i cha
NK016(ma)011:95: byad can gyis dbu ba rgyan par bsam /
NK016(ma)011:96: slar yang spyi bor zla ba la dkar po /
NK016(ma)011:98: snying gar nyi ma la h'u sngon po /
NK016(ma)011:99: de gsum las 'phros pa'i 'od zer kyis rdo rje
NK016(ma)011:100: gsum gyi lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar spyan drangs
NK016(ma)011:101: te yi ge so so la thim pas de bzhin
NK016(ma)011:102: gshegs pa thams cad kyi rdo rje gsum dang gnyis
NK016(ma)011:104: yi ge so so yongs su gyur pa las /
NK016(ma)011:105: spyi bor sku rdo rje dkar po 'khor lo /
NK016(ma)011:106: mgrin par gsung rjo rje dmar po pad+ma /
NK016(ma)011:107: snying gar thugs rdo rje sngon po rdo rje 'dzin pa rnams kyis rgyas btab par bsam /
NK016(ma)011:108: slar yang snying ga'i h'u gi 'od zer gyis phyogs
NK016(ma)011:109: bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa mkha'
NK016(ma)011:110: khyab tu sad pa rang la dbyer med du 'dres
NK016(ma)011:111: par bsam la yang yang bzla ba ni ye shes
NK016(ma)011:112: sems dpa' bskyar bsnan gyi sbyor ba dang /
NK016(ma)011:113: de nas lha sku'i gsal snang la sems rtse gcig tu bzung zhing /
NK016(ma)011:114: res zhu bdes drangs pa'i bde stong gi lha skur 'char ba la slob pa dang /
NK016(ma)011:115: yang rang sems lhag pa bden gnyis dbyer med kyi
NK016(ma)011:116: lha'i skur rnam par dag pa'i nges shes bskyed la
NK016(ma)011:117: bskyang ngo // gnyis pa sngags bzla ba ni /
NK016(ma)011:118: thugs ka'i h'u yig gi mthar yi ge brgya pa'i
NK016(ma)011:119: sngags phreng kha dog dkar po g.yas bskor du 'khor
NK016(ma)011:120: ba / de las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskul /
NK016(ma)011:121: bdag dang mkha' khyab kyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK016(ma)011:122: cad kyi zhal nas sngags kyi sgra dang thugs rje'i
NK016(ma)011:123: 'od zer 'phros pas khams gsum thams cad snang bar
NK016(ma)011:124: byas / las dang nyon mongs pa thams cad sbyangs /
NK016(ma)011:125: na rag sogs ngan song gi gnas rnams dong nas sprugs te /
NK016(ma)011:126: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing du bsgral /
NK016(ma)011:127: 'od zer rnams slar 'dus te sngags phreng la thim /
NK016(ma)011:128: snang grags 'gyu gsum lha sngags 'od gsal gyi 'khor lor sad par mos la /
NK016(ma)011:129: yig brgya'i dzapa nyer gcig las mi nyung bar bazla'o //
NK016(ma)011:133: dang po thun bsdu ba ni /
NK016(ma)011:134: snod bcud kyi snang ba thams cad 'od du zhu ba rang la thim /
NK016(ma)011:135: rang ye shes sems dpa' la /
NK016(ma)011:136: de ting nge 'dzin sems dpa' h'u la /
NK016(ma)011:137: h'u gyen rdzogs n+aa da'i bar du thim nas rnam
NK016(ma)011:138: par rtog med lhun grub nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang
NK016(ma)011:141: slar yang rang nyid dpal rdo rje sems dpa' snang
NK016(ma)011:142: stong sgyu ma lta bu'i skur gyur pa'i spyi bor
NK016(ma)011:143: / mgrin par +aah snying gar h'u yig gis mtshan pa /
NK016(ma)011:144: lus rdo rje'i go chas zhu lugs su g.yogs pas
NK016(ma)011:145: sgo gsum rdo rje gsum dang dbyer mi phyed par
NK016(ma)011:147: spyod lam thams cad lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi rol par spyad do //
NK016(ma)011:149: dge ba 'di yis myur du bdag /
NK016(ma)011:150: rdo rje sems dpa' 'grub gyur nas //
NK016(ma)011:151: 'gro ba gcig kyang ma lus pa //
NK016(ma)011:152: de yi sa la 'god par shog /
NK016(ma)011:154: shis brjod ji ltar rigs pas mtha' brgyan par bya'o //
NK016(ma)011:156: rgya'i sngags ston bsod nams chos kyi rgyal mtshan nas
NK016(ma)011:157: bskul bar mdzad pa las dong sprugs rtsa ba'i khrid
NK016(ma)011:158: yig gi snying po don gyi bcud phyungs te 'jigs
NK016(ma)011:159: bral ye shes rdo rjes sbyar ba dge legs su
